Heat oven to 350 degrees F. In 10-inch skillet cook bacon on medium-high heat until crisp. Drain grease; crumble bacon. In medium bowl combine Simply Potatoes(R), cream cheese, bacon and salt; stir to mix well. Spoon about 2/3 cup Simply Potatoes(R) mixture into 6 (1 cup) glass custard cups or ramekins. Top each with 1 tablespoon cheese. Sprinkle lightly with paprika. Bake 15 to 20 minutes or until heated through. Garnish each with chopped fresh chives.